### Get all region preferences
GET {{BASE_URL}}/region-preferences

### Get a single region preference by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/region-preferences/1

### Create a new region preference
POST {{BASE_URL}}/region-preferences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "regionId": 1,
  "preferred": true
}

### Update a region preference by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/region-preferences/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "preferred": false
}

### Delete a region preference by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/region-preferences/1
